<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Allen Telecom started.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Allen Telecom started.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-07-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Genesis Merchant Group Securities said analyst Charles Thomas initiated coverage of Allen Telecom Inc with a long-term buy recommendation.</p>
<p>-- Thomas set earnings per share estimates for 1997 on the company of $1.15 on revenue of $449 million, and $1.45 on revenue of $541 million for 1998.</p>
<p>-- the stock was up 1/8 at 20-3/4.</p>
